- Let's go.
- I can't stand it.

32
00:01:02,232 --> 00:01:03,901
- Keep going.
- Hi, everyone!

33
00:01:03,902 --> 00:01:05,302
Get out of your cars and watch.

34
00:01:06,042 --> 00:01:08,072
That's it. Come and watch.

35
00:01:08,212 --> 00:01:09,642
