67
00:02:14,312 --> 00:02:15,341
At Korea National University of Arts?

68
00:02:15,342 --> 00:02:17,481
At Korea National University of Arts. It's hard to believe,

69
00:02:17,482 --> 00:02:19,782
but I swear, they teach you this move.

70
00:02:19,852 --> 00:02:22,011
