176
00:05:39,042 --> 00:05:40,751
(War of Idiots: Odd Man Out Versus Average Idiots)

177
00:05:40,752 --> 00:05:42,111
- The War of Idiots?
- The War of Idiots?

178
00:05:42,112 --> 00:05:43,322
- What?
- That's so insulting.

179
00:05:43,852 --> 00:05:45,082
The War of Idiots?

180
00:05:45,252 --> 00:05:46,652
