And make mistakes.

1021
00:33:40,088 --> 00:33:41,518
Let's set a mousetrap.

1022
00:33:42,158 --> 00:33:44,928
Catch the mouse, squeak

1023
00:33:45,758 --> 00:33:47,757
(Soon, they arrive at Gapyeong Rest Stop.)

1024
00:33:47,758 --> 00:33:49,718
Everyone, we're here. We have to catch the mouse.

1025
00:33:49,858 --> 00:33:51,498
- We're here.
- We're here.

1026
00:33:51,698 --> 00:33:52,898
I'm getting impatient.

1027
00:33:53,468 --> 00:33:54,767
Yes, we're here.

1028
00:33:54,768 --> 00:33:56,997
