Has DinDin stopped by?

1044
00:34:26,128 --> 00:34:27,967
(A spinning wheel with food names?)

1045
00:34:27,968 --> 00:34:29,268
What? Was DinDin already here?

1046
00:34:29,638 --> 00:34:31,468
DinDin is over there.

1047
00:34:31,908 --> 00:34:32,968
There he is.

1048
00:34:33,468 --> 00:34:35,137
