1052
00:34:40,678 --> 00:34:42,517
- We're at Gapyeong Rest Stop.
- Yes.

1053
00:34:42,518 --> 00:34:45,887
Your mission here is called One Bite in Silence.

1054
00:34:45,888 --> 00:34:47,534
- I took too much time.
- Do you see this?

1055
00:34:47,558 --> 00:34:50,658
Throw a dart at the spinning wheel to pick a dish.

1056
00:34:51,528 --> 00:34:54,858
(Throw a dart at the spinning wheel to pick a dish.)

1057
00:34:54,998 --> 00:34:57,198
Get a citizen to share it with you.

1058
00:34:57,498 --> 00:34:58,627
(A difficult mission even to One-Bite Race veterans)

1059
00:34:58,628 --> 00:35:00,968
- This is hard.
- However,

1060
00:35:01,638 --> 00:35:03,538
