1061
00:35:03,798 --> 00:35:06,037
- "Ah" is all you need.
- Yes, and so...

1062
00:35:06,038 --> 00:35:07,038
(Getting treated by a citizen without explanation except "ah")

1063
00:35:07,039 --> 00:35:08,677
- There are four of us.
- Yes.

1064
00:35:08,678 --> 00:35:09,907
Is it okay if only one of us succeeds?

1065
00:35:09,908 --> 00:35:11,677
- Of course not.
- All of you have to succeed.

1066
00:35:11,678 --> 00:35:12,678
What?

1067
00:35:12,679 --> 00:35:13,807
(You're one team.)

1068
00:35:13,808 --> 00:35:16,778
Two of you can't ask the same citizen.

1069
00:35:17,248 --> 00:35:18,817
Okay, since we're hungry,

1070
00:35:18,818 --> 00:35:20,557
- let's get treated.
- Once everyone succeeds,

1071
00:35:20,558 --> 00:35:23,257
- I'll have to get food.
- we'll give you a hint.

1072
00:35:23,258 --> 00:35:24,288
Okay.

1073
00:35:24,588 --> 00:35:26,688
- I'll start.
- Spin the wheel.

1074
00:35:26,928 --> 00:35:28,597
- I'll start.
- Go ahead.

1075
00:35:28,598 --> 00:35:30,698
- Where is it? That's right.
- What is it?

1076
00:35:31,028 --> 00:35:32,304
- It's walnut cake.
- It's walnut cake.

1077
00:35:32,328 --> 00:35:33,998
- Walnut cake. Go.
- Shall I go?

1078
00:35:34,568 --> 00:35:37,237
