(Jong Min's turn)

1090
00:35:59,058 --> 00:36:00,428
- Tteokbokki.
- Tteokbokki.

1091
00:36:01,228 --> 00:36:03,498
(Korean people's comfort food)

1092
00:36:03,658 --> 00:36:05,027
A bite of tteokbokki? That's good.

1093
00:36:05,028 --> 00:36:07,198
What's DinDin's? Take a look.

1094
00:36:07,998 --> 00:36:08,998
