1095
00:36:08,999 --> 00:36:10,838
- Is it walnut cake?
- No, it's corn dog.

1096
00:36:11,108 --> 00:36:12,407
- Corn dog? Okay.
- Corn dog.

1097
00:36:12,408 --> 00:36:13,408
(He agrees without a fuss.)

1098
00:36:13,409 --> 00:36:14,677
Since I have a certain image,

1099
00:36:14,678 --> 00:36:15,937
