1100
00:36:15,938 --> 00:36:16,938
(The mission starts.)

1101
00:36:17,408 --> 00:36:18,507
Walnut cake.

1102
00:36:18,508 --> 00:36:20,247
(Seon Ho's mission is getting a bite of walnut cake.)

1103
00:36:20,248 --> 00:36:22,478
First, I have to find someone who's eating walnut cake.

1104
00:36:23,648 --> 00:36:25,017
There's a walnut cake shop over there.

1105
00:36:25,018 --> 00:36:26,187
(He spots a walnut cake shop.)

1106
00:36:26,188 --> 00:36:27,488
I'll go there first.

1107
00:36:28,088 --> 00:36:29,857
Hello.

1108
00:36:29,858 --> 00:36:30,927
Hello.

1109
00:36:30,928 --> 00:36:32,928
(A citizen says hello with excitement.)

1110
00:36:33,388 --> 00:36:34,498
Isn't that walnut cake?

1111
00:36:35,728 --> 00:36:38,128
(A bag of walnut cake?)

1112
00:36:38,568 --> 00:36:41,367
