1113
00:36:41,368 --> 00:36:42,667
(Turning around suddenly)

1114
00:36:42,668 --> 00:36:45,437
Are you okay with being on camera for a minute?

1115
00:36:45,438 --> 00:36:46,937
(He tries to cast her right away.)

1116
00:36:46,938 --> 00:36:48,277
- Is that okay?
- Yes, it's fine.

1117
00:36:48,278 --> 00:36:49,478
Is it okay?

1118
00:36:49,508 --> 00:36:51,178
- Hello.
- Hello.

1119
00:36:51,548 --> 00:36:52,578
(Opening his mouth)

1120
00:36:52,948 --> 00:36:54,347
(Attempting the mission out of nowhere)

1121
00:36:54,348 --> 00:36:55,418
Sure.

1122
00:36:56,448 --> 00:36:58,418
(Will he succeed the mission right away?)

1123
00:36:58,518 --> 00:37:00,278
(As if possessed, she puts it in his mouth.)

1124
00:37:00,318 --> 00:37:01,518
Thank you.

1125
00:37:01,888 --> 00:37:02,958
Have some.

1126
00:37:03,088 --> 00:37:06,058
