1128
00:37:09,228 --> 00:37:11,497
It's a little present for you.

1129
00:37:11,498 --> 00:37:13,097
- Seriously?
- Yes.

1130
00:37:13,098 --> 00:37:14,697
- Is it okay to accept it?
- You gave me a bite.

1131
00:37:14,698 --> 00:37:16,537
- Really?
- Thank you.

1132
00:37:16,538 --> 00:37:17,807
- You're welcome.
- It must have been a mission.

1133
00:37:17,808 --> 00:37:19,307
Yes, it was a mission. Thank you.

1134
00:37:19,308 --> 00:37:20,737
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

1135
00:37:20,738 --> 00:37:22,177
I can do this. Thank you.

1136
00:37:22,178 --> 00:37:24,108
(Seon Ho is the first one to succeed.)

1137
00:37:25,148 --> 00:37:28,678
(Joon's mission is getting a bite of ramyeon.)

1138
