(Giving a bite of ramyeon even to family is hard.)

1139
00:37:31,618 --> 00:37:33,388
(Will he succeed?)

1140
00:37:35,918 --> 00:37:39,058
(Going straight to a citizen who's eating)

1141
00:37:39,328 --> 00:37:41,598
(Luckily, they're eating ramyeon.)

1142
00:37:41,758 --> 00:37:42,897
Hello.

1143
00:37:42,898 --> 00:37:43,898
(Polite)

1144
00:37:44,928 --> 00:37:47,198
(The citizen greets him happily.)

1145
00:37:47,268 --> 00:37:48,698
(Opening his mouth)

1146
00:37:49,698 --> 00:37:51,767
(How could this young man...)

1147
00:37:51,768 --> 00:37:53,008
