1150
00:37:58,178 --> 00:37:59,178
Do you want some?

1151
00:37:59,179 --> 00:38:00,377
(Nodding)

1152
00:38:00,378 --> 00:38:03,677
(There's nothing left. I'm so sorry.)

1153
00:38:03,678 --> 00:38:05,587
(Would you like some broth at least?)

1154
00:38:05,588 --> 00:38:06,888
Oh, no.

1155
00:38:06,918 --> 00:38:08,958
Thank you. I succeeded immediately.

1156
00:38:09,488 --> 00:38:11,927
We're shooting 2 Days 1 Night, and I could only say "ah."

1157
00:38:11,928 --> 00:38:14,928
This is a free gift for you.

1158
00:38:15,198 --> 00:38:18,767
- It's a gift from 2 Days 1 Night.
- You don't have to.

1159
00:38:18,768 --> 00:38:21,537
- I watch your show all the time.
- Thank you.

1160
00:38:21,538 --> 00:38:22,697
2 Days...

1161
00:38:22,698 --> 00:38:23,898
- 1 Night.
- 1 Night.

1162
00:38:24,268 --> 00:38:26,337
- It's a day worth celebrating.
- Thank you.

1163
00:38:26,338 --> 00:38:29,177
I'm so happy to meet you. This is amazing.

1164
00:38:29,178 --> 00:38:30,678
Thank you. Have a good day.

1165
00:38:30,948 --> 00:38:32,178
Thank you.

1166
00:38:32,478 --> 00:38:34,008
I succeeded right away.

1167
00:38:34,678 --> 00:38:37,217
