1168
00:38:37,218 --> 00:38:38,818
- There it is.
- Let's get in the car...

1169
00:38:38,948 --> 00:38:40,987
- and put on the seat belt.
- Get ready to go.

1170
00:38:40,988 --> 00:38:41,988
Get inside and wait.

1171
00:38:42,058 --> 00:38:43,757
- We haven't peed yet.
- That's what we should do.

1172
00:38:43,758 --> 00:38:45,487
- I haven't peed yet.
- Right.

1173
00:38:45,488 --> 00:38:47,427
If one of us goes to the restroom, everyone has to wait.

1174
00:38:47,428 --> 00:38:48,497
(Just hold it for now.)

1175
00:38:48,498 --> 00:38:49,498
Let's get in.

1176
00:38:49,499 --> 00:38:50,627
(Joon and Seon Ho are ready to leave.)

1177
00:38:50,628 --> 00:38:51,908
- I'll start the engine.
- Okay.

1178
00:38:52,298 --> 00:38:55,668
