- DinDin, I'm your fan.

1183
00:39:03,408 --> 00:39:06,307
- Let me go.
- DinDin, I'm your huge fan.

1184
00:39:06,308 --> 00:39:08,547
Okay, I'll take my time.

1185
00:39:08,548 --> 00:39:10,517
- Let me go.
- You went to Canada.

1186
00:39:10,518 --> 00:39:14,457
- DinDin.
- I'll take my time.

1187
00:39:14,458 --> 00:39:16,458
I will take my time. I promise.

1188
00:39:18,558 --> 00:39:21,958
(As soon as Se Yoon lets him go, he dashes off.)

1189
00:39:22,258 --> 00:39:23,397
Hello.

1190
00:39:23,398 --> 00:39:26,328
(Scanning the tables)

1191
00:39:27,298 --> 00:39:30,098
(He can't find anyone eating a corn dog.)

1192
00:39:30,868 --> 00:39:34,038
