1196
00:39:43,348 --> 00:39:44,348
Hello.

1197
00:39:45,148 --> 00:39:48,488
Hello, we're shooting 2 Days 1 Night.

1198
00:39:49,018 --> 00:39:51,457
- Could you... I'm DinDin.
- Gosh. Aren't you DinDin?

1199
00:39:51,458 --> 00:39:52,458
My goodness.

1200
00:39:52,459 --> 00:39:54,697
- What's this?
- It's an old-fashioned corn dog.

1201
00:39:54,698 --> 00:39:57,357
- What's this?
- It's a sausage.

1202
00:39:57,358 --> 00:39:58,798
A sausage? This is a corn dog?

1203
00:39:59,368 --> 00:40:00,768
(Opening his mouth)

1204
00:40:01,098 --> 00:40:02,368
(Flustered)

1205
00:40:03,268 --> 00:40:05,408
(Will DinDin also succeed in one try?)

1206
00:40:06,568 --> 00:40:08,007
Wait, that's it.

1207
00:40:08,008 --> 00:40:09,807
(Se Yoon is in front of the walnut cake shop.)

1208
00:40:09,808 --> 00:40:12,207
I should try some walnut cake with pine nuts.

1209
00:40:12,208 --> 00:40:14,007
