1210
00:40:14,008 --> 00:40:15,218
Walnut cake with pine nuts.

1211
00:40:15,548 --> 00:40:16,818
Hello.

1212
00:40:16,948 --> 00:40:19,018
(He spots a citizen who bought some walnut cake.)

1213
00:40:19,048 --> 00:40:20,048
Hello.

1214
00:40:20,388 --> 00:40:22,888
Is walnut cake with pine nuts good?

1215
00:40:23,988 --> 00:40:24,988
Ma'am.

1216
00:40:24,989 --> 00:40:26,464
(She chooses to return home quickly.)

1217
00:40:26,488 --> 00:40:27,488
(Ma'am)

1218
00:40:28,428 --> 00:40:31,098
(Unexpectedly, his first attempt fails.)

1219
00:40:32,728 --> 00:40:35,138
Goodness. How will I eat someone's food?

1220
00:40:35,538 --> 00:40:37,567
- Would you like some of this?
- No, it's okay.

1221
00:40:37,568 --> 00:40:40,168
This isn't what I'm looking for.

1222
00:40:42,108 --> 00:40:43,708
Hello, where are you going?

1223
00:40:44,548 --> 00:40:45,707
May I talk to you?

1224
00:40:45,708 --> 00:40:46,807
- Yes.
- Really?

1225
00:40:46,808 --> 00:40:49,247
We're shooting 2 Days 1 Night. Do you mind being on camera?

1226
00:40:49,248 --> 00:40:50,777
- Is it possible? Really?
- Yes.

1227
00:40:50,778 --> 00:40:52,487
Nice to meet you. Where are you going?

1228
00:40:52,488 --> 00:40:54,017
You bought so much walnut cake.

1229
00:40:54,018 --> 00:40:55,288
I'm going to visit my parents.

1230
00:40:55,388 --> 00:40:56,517
(I see.)

1231
00:40:56,518 --> 00:40:59,127
They like walnut cake, so I came here to buy it.

1232
00:40:59,128 --> 00:41:00,128
(Opening his mouth)

1233
00:41:00,129 --> 00:41:02,257
(His "ah" makes us think that he wants an entire bag.)

1234
00:41:02,258 --> 00:41:04,327
I'm your fan. Gosh.

1235
00:41:04,328 --> 00:41:05,967
I'm your fan. Gosh.

1236
00:41:05,968 --> 00:41:08,338
(Opening his mouth as big as he can without caring)

1237
00:41:10,098 --> 00:41:11,737
Would you like a bag?

1238
00:41:11,738 --> 00:41:13,237
