1932
01:05:16,046 --> 01:05:17,186
Seriously...

1933
01:05:17,786 --> 01:05:19,955
I really want to drink while eating makguksu.

1934
01:05:19,956 --> 01:05:22,237
(It's packed with rich flavor when mixed with the broth.)

1935
01:05:24,586 --> 01:05:25,696
This is really good.

1936
01:05:25,826 --> 01:05:27,355
This is the season for this.

1937
01:05:27,356 --> 01:05:28,625
