1938
01:05:28,626 --> 01:05:30,265
- I get what you mean.
- Dakgalbi and makguksu...

1939
01:05:30,266 --> 01:05:32,195
don't really have a season, but right now...

1940
01:05:32,196 --> 01:05:34,136
