1971
01:06:32,656 --> 01:06:34,396
How did you know "artificial?"

1972
01:06:34,526 --> 01:06:35,725
Why wouldn't I? I'm good at English.

1973
01:06:35,726 --> 01:06:38,626
Joon keeps studying English.

1974
01:06:39,236 --> 01:06:41,595
You'd have improved a lot if you spent a day with me.

1975
01:06:41,596 --> 01:06:42,806
Right. It's different.

1976
01:06:42,966 --> 01:06:44,705
I told you. I tried to warn you.

1977
01:06:44,706 --> 01:06:45,876
Artificial.

1978
01:06:46,736 --> 01:06:47,875
How is it? Is it sweet?

1979
01:06:47,876 --> 01:06:49,105
(Taking a bite of the dakgalbi)

1980
01:06:49,106 --> 01:06:50,176
Is it very good?

1981
01:06:51,606 --> 01:06:53,876
- The broth tastes amazing.
- It tastes great like this.

1982
01:06:54,446 --> 01:06:57,646
I've got some surprising news.

1983
01:06:58,386 --> 01:06:59,386
That startled me.

1984
01:06:59,586 --> 01:07:01,056
What could be surprising?

1985
01:07:01,356 --> 01:07:02,957
