- Yes.

1990
01:07:11,717 --> 01:07:13,556
- That's right.
- So...

1991
01:07:13,557 --> 01:07:16,257
- It's important.
- Let's do our best.

1992
01:07:16,557 --> 01:07:18,156
When I say "catch the mouse,"

1993
01:07:18,157 --> 01:07:19,796
